      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Two Approaches to State Management\n\nCrewAI offers two ways to manage state in your flows:\n\nUnstructured State - Using dictionary-like objects for flexibility\n\nStructured State - Using Pydantic models for type safety and validation\nLet’s examine each approach in detail.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Two Approaches to State Management\n\nCrewAI offers two ways to manage state in your flows:\n\nUnstructured State - Using dictionary-like objects for flexibility\n\nStructured State - Using Pydantic models for type safety and validation\nLet’s examine each approach in detail.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
